How to use dynamic ROI placement (20230630 - Sca)
use the same parameters in all XY seams of one weld area (eg 5, 9 or 10 welds per area and Precitec product)
parameterize tables G13 & G14 for positions P01 to P10 for X and Y in px respectively do this in a neutral angle position (0deg)-> template for fiducial detection needs to be in a neutral angle
if you do not have the option to measure the px offsets from TCP use P10 angle offset for ROI placement parameter and input the negative value of the output Hairpin Value 10 as parameter for this parameter
check if positions are correct with images in various angle positions

Detection templates for Hairpin detection: (20230630 - Sca)
templates for Hairpin detection need to be snipped in weld area 4
Fiducial templates use area 4 for fiducial template if this is nbot possible - use angle offset for dynamic ROI placement
